thread.title: Angelica Huynh

author: Angelica Huynh
title: Angelica Huynh
text: Since I'm asian and live in Sweden, I rarely find any products related to Asia which can be frustrating since my skintype would fit those products the best. With YesStyle I can buy almost everything I want from the Asian market for a great price. I ordered from them once before, and I got the deliviery in just 2,5 weeks which is amazing since it's the other side of the world. Love this shop.
